Package: SplinesUtils
Version: 0.1-1
Date: 2018-10-07
Title: Utility functions for univariate cubic interpolation splines, smoothing splines and regression B-splines
Author: Zheyuan Li <zheyuan.li@bath.edu>
Maintainer: Zheyuan Li <zheyuan.li@bath.edu>
Depends: R (>= 3.4.0), splines
Imports: stats, graphics
Description: Reparametrize univariate cubic interpolation splines, smoothing splines and regression B-splines as piecewise polynomials. Export polynomial coefficients as a matrix and print polynomial equations as formatted strings. Plot and predict a spline or its derivatives. Solve a spline or its derivatives for a given value.
License: GPL-3
NeedsCompilation: no
